name: Astral Seconds
description:
As in any big city we cannot see everything that the sky hides due to light pollution, that is why it is inevitable to remember the first sky I saw with so many stars, as a child I did not imagine how incredible the starry sky looks and even today it still amazes me, that's why when I have the opportunity to photograph the sky I don't hesitate to do it.

That is why today I want to show you the sky that at times managed to hide the clouds, some constellations and shooting stars could be seen, the galactic center was very elusive, but as soon as I have the opportunity I promise to do my duty to do my best effort for you. Thank you for your support
